g.text: Expand-Contract pattern with Neon branches
Production Environment Rollout: Phased & Monitored
1. DEV: Expand Phase - Introduce New Schema
2. DEV: Migrate Phase - Shift Application Reads
3. DEV: Contract Phase - Remove Old Schema
4. PROD: Expand Phase - Introduce New Schema
5. PROD: Migrate Phase - Shift Application Reads
6. PROD: Contract Phase - Remove Old Schema

text.tspan: 1.1 Schema: Add 'new_column' (col_N) to table in schema.ts.
Old 'old_column' (col_O) remains.

g.text: 1.2 Drizzle: Generate 'add col_N' migration files.

text.tspan: 1.3 Neon Dev Branch: Apply 'add col_N' migration.
Schema now has col_O and col_N.
1.4 Dev App: Deploy code for DUAL WRITE.
App writes to BOTH col_O & col_N.
App still READS ONLY from col_O.
1.5 Neon Dev Branch: Backfill data from col_O to col_N.
(e.g., UPDATE table SET col_N = col_O).

g.text: 1.6 Test Dev: Verify dual writes, data backfill, and app reads (still from col_O).

text.tspan: 2.1 Dev App: Deploy code to READ from 'new_column' (col_N).
Writes ideally continue to BOTH col_O & col_N for safety.

g.text: 2.2 Test Dev: Verify app reads correctly from col_N and all functionality is intact.

text.tspan: 3.1 Dev App: Deploy code to write ONLY to 'new_column' (col_N).
Stop writing to 'old_column' (col_O).

g.text: 3.2 Schema: Remove 'old_column' (col_O) from schema.ts.
3.3 Drizzle: Generate 'drop col_O' migration files.

text.tspan: 3.4 Neon Dev Branch: Apply 'drop col_O' migration.
Schema now only has col_N.

g.text: 3.5 Test Dev: Full regression test. Verify app works exclusively with col_N.
4.1 Neon Prod DB: Apply validated 'add col_N' migration.

text.tspan: 4.2 Prod App: Deploy validated DUAL WRITE code.
(Writes: col_O + col_N, Reads: col_O).
4.3 Neon Prod DB: Execute data backfill (col_N from col_O).
Monitor performance & completion.

g.text: 4.4 Monitor Prod: Observe application health and data consistency.
5.1 Prod App: Deploy validated code to READ from 'new_column' (col_N).
5.2 Monitor Prod: Check read patterns, performance, and data accuracy.
6.1 Prod App: Deploy validated code to write ONLY to 'new_column' (col_N).

text.tspan: 6.2 Neon Prod DB: Apply validated 'drop col_O' migration.
(After app is fully transitioned).

g.text: 6.3 Monitor Prod: Final system health check.
Validate Next Phase
Validate Next Phase
Rollout Next Phase
Rollout Next Phase
Begin Phased Production Rollout
